VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT addJavascriptInterface\s*\(
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:addJavascriptInterface && PRESENT:setAllowFileAccessFromFileURLs\s*\(\s*true|setAllowUniversalAccessFromFileURLs\s*\(\s*true
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the dangerous combination of addJavascriptInterface and file URL access enabled in the same WebView configuration.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for addJavascriptInterface with File Access Enabled.
